    pol:hasText "without prejudice to paragraph 7, the permit-granting process referred to in paragraph 1 shall not exceed two years for power plants, including all relevant procedures of competent authorities. where duly justified on the grounds of extraordinary circumstances, that two-year period may be extended by up to one year." .

